title: Ep. 63: Wild-Card Weekend Preview
description:
The Ringer's Robert Mays and Danny Kelly preview the Raiders visiting the Texans (1:16), Detroit going to Seattle (11:01), Miami at Pittsburgh (21:35), and the Giants against the Packers (31:12).
